metadata.name: Davud Abbas
metadata.description:
1/1 minted by Hulki Okan Tabak, Digital Persona smart contract, 2023

Digital Persona is an AI photography project that creates the images solely from text prompts in the first phase. Then the previous images become training input for the next phase. Each phase incorporates brand new generations from scratch as well as from training. Digital Persona is initially minted on its own Manifold deployed smart contract. Next steps will be Foundation Drops and mints on other platforms.
